item.title: How to change teleport coords and name of tele
item.dc:creator: @Sivan Sivan
item.description:
@Sivan wrote:

1: To change name text.java
2: Ctr+f current name, Then edit it.

1: Changing tele coords clickingmost.java
2: Search for the current coords.
3: Then go clickingmost.java ctr+f.
4: Then edit it to the coords you want.
